name: Fieldset.Root
description: A set of form controls optionally grouped under a common name.
description_zh: A set of form controls optionally grouped under a common name.

asChild.description: Use the provided child element as the default rendered element, combining their props and behavior.
asChild.description_zh: 使用提供的子元素作为默认渲染元素，结合它们的 props 和行为。

disabled.description: Indicates whether the fieldset is disabled.
disabled.description_zh: 指示字段集是否被禁用。

invalid.description: Indicates whether the fieldset is invalid.
